snippet.title: Status One | New Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Status One is a top-down 3D tactical shooter where you create your own task force from scratch and lead your squad while being personally on the field

Our game is finally on steam, you can go there and wishlist it now, 

Wishlist Now Here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2598610?utm_source=yt1

Music by Karl Casey @ White Bat Audio | Phantoms
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r5pCKclD_XA
